  "excerpt": "Beef Bourguignon. A home-cook's recipe from Rebecca's collection, kept in the family rotation.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "From Rebecca's personal cookbook. The dish sits in the classical French slow-cook tradition, Escoffier, Larousse Gastronomique, and the home-cookery tradition of southwest France.",
  "body": {
