      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Beef Bourguignon. Classical French method, scaled to a home kitchen. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A weeknight-friendly recipe: most of the work is the prep, and the cooking takes care of itself.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
